>>50914390
believe it or not, roxy is the mother of all female skate club models. i used her topo as a base for ashley, then morgan, and so on, adjusting a few proportions and model topology for each charatcer to match their clothes and accessories. i keep an unrigged and rigged version of every character. when a new character is made, i almost always use the unrigged model, mirror modifyer, re-work the topo, draw a new texture sheet, replace the texture, then rig the new model using rigify. sometimes it takes a while but it's very fun to give each and every character their own colors and theme. imagination is the limit. if it helps, you can find a few of the game models here: https://gitlab.com/spacedimsum
